content = "[b]Lost Scout Notes - Page 2 of 3[/b]\\n\\nYou found page 2! Great navigation skills!\\n\\n[b]Navigation Tip:[/b] Always note landmarks. The sun rises in the [b]east[/b] and sets in the [b]west[/b]. Your compass shows true north.\\n\\nWhen lost, remember STOP:\\n• [b]S[/b]top - don't panic\\n• [b]T[/b]hink - what do you know?\\n• [b]O[/b]bserve - look around for landmarks\\n• [b]P[/b]lan - decide the safest route\\n\\nOne more page to find! Check [b]southwest[/b] near the river.\\n- Kofi"
collect_sound_effect = ExtResource("3_p3g4h")
item_data = SubResource("Resource_bp2data")
